# UI Components

Reusable UI elements are located in `src/components`.

- **Core Components:** Application-specific components like `[Timer.tsx](mdc:src/components/Timer.tsx)`, `[SessionHistory.tsx](mdc:src/components/SessionHistory.tsx)`, `[Charts.tsx](mdc:src/components/Charts.tsx)`, `[Achievements.tsx](mdc:src/components/Achievements.tsx)`, `[UserMenu.tsx](mdc:src/components/UserMenu.tsx)`, etc., reside directly in `[src/components](mdc:src/components)`.
- **shadcn/ui Primitives:** Base UI primitives provided by `shadcn/ui` (e.g., Button, Card, Dialog) are located in `[src/components/ui](mdc:src/components/ui)`. These are typically added via the `shadcn-ui` CLI and can be customized there.
- **Theme Toggle:** Dark/light mode switching is handled by `[mode-toggle.tsx](mdc:src/components/mode-toggle.tsx)` and configured via `[theme-provider.tsx](mdc:src/components/theme-provider.tsx)`.
